title: S2 E4: Zero to Murder in 60 Seconds
description:
This week, Maggie & Tim podcast the shit out of another episode. Season 2 Episode 4 to be exact. In this ep, Shawn tracks down a stolen car, but then realizes there's more to the case than meets the eye! Plus, Jules & Lassi have an adorable photoshoot for a special presentation at 21 LES.
